high_descs: Turn left, go to face the trash can past the counter on the right.
Pick up the egg in the trash can.
Bring the egg to the microwave on the right.
Heat the egg in the microwave.
Take the heated egg back to the trash can on the left of the counter.
Put the heated egg in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the gray bin on the floor next to the fridge on the right.
Pick up the egg from inside the gray bin on the floor.
Turn around, take a left and walk to the microwave on the left above the counter.
Put the egg inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, take a right and face the gray bin on the floor to the right.
Put the heated egg in the gray bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated egg in a bin.
